data.description: This recently built stunner is listed below tax assessor's market value yet offers an abundance of elegant and tasteful finishes amidst a well desiged floorplan that provides multiple opportunities for family gatherings or quiet time with a good book. Built in 2019,  this 4 bedroom, 3 full bath gem is Pulte's Mesilla floorplan *and* it offers their exquisite Front Elevation R, which boasts full brick front with a soaring 2-story limestone accent entryway.  Step inside to an open concept living/dining/kitchen BUT with the added functionality of a home office with French doors to the right just off your expansive dining room as well as a side hallway that leads to a good-sized bedroom and full bath. (Perfect for inlaws who prefer the first floor).  Continue into the grand living area and to your left you'll discover a spacious, gorgeous kitchen in stylish gray hues with wraparound cabinetry and gorgeous granite counters. There is even a center island, a full sized pantry and space for a breakfast table. Head up stairs and you'll be welcomed by a large playroom/gameroom/secondary living room. The owner's suite is to your right and it is fitted with a celing fan and more recessed lighting. A spa-like Primary Bath offers a soaking tub, separate walk-in shower dual vanities and a massive walk-in closet. Down the hall on the other side of the staircase are two secondary bedrooms, plus a full bathroom and a laundry room. This lovely home truly is ready to move in. This beautiful home also offers an upgraded & expanded concrete patio in a huge backyard that is ready for you to make your own. ***Washer dryer convey! And select furniture pieces are offered with the home: Dining table, buffet, LR leather couches, end tables & coffee tables. Basically all LR furniture EXCEPT the TV & TV stand)***
